            "detailed_description": "The Yellow Quiz - a fun multiplayer game for parties that turns your smartphone into a wireless game controller. It's simple: You'll only need your smartphones and a TV or any other big Screen. The Yellow Quiz comes with three simple and fun game modes:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Classical Quiz:</strong> Square off in a classic Multiple Choice Quiz against your friends.<br></li><li> <strong>Guess Roulette:</strong> Pick a number that best answers the question and place a bet on it. The correct number isn't always picked but the closer you get the better are your chances.<br></li><li> <strong>Drawing :</strong> Draw something on a prompt and let your friends guess what you meant.</li></ul><br>The Yellow Quiz requires each player to have the <strong>free</strong> Controller App (see <strong>Website</strong> or <strong>Manual</strong>) in order to be played.",
